---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Refund Policy - OPTYP" 
  description="Comprehensive and transparent Refund Policy for OPTYP’s professional resume and profile optimization services, aligned with international consumer protection standards.">

  <section class="relative py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-gray-900 to-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl font-body">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-white">Refund Policy</h1>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-green-500 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          At OPTYP, we value your trust and aim to deliver professional services that meet or exceed expectations. This Refund Policy ensures transparency in all financial matters.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-300 space-y-12">

        <!-- Eligibility -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Refund Eligibility</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl">
            <p class="font-semibold mb-4">Refunds may be approved under the following conditions:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Timeframe:</strong> Requests submitted within <span class="text-yellow-300 font-semibold">7 days</span> of delivery.</li>
              <li><strong>Service Issues:</strong> Undelivered or incomplete services due to provider error.</li>
              <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> Failure to deliver on agreed timelines without communication.</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Errors:</strong> Major issues caused by system or platform malfunctions.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-6 glass-box border border-red-500/40 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400 mb-3">Services Not Eligible for Refund</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-red-300">
                <li>Completed and client-approved projects.</li>
                <li>Change of mind or personal preference after delivery.</li>
                <li>Unrealistic job or interview outcomes (beyond our control).</li>
                <li>Requests submitted after 7 days of delivery.</li>
                <li>Custom or add-on services outside the standard package.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-sm">
              Please note: As our services involve personalized digital deliverables, once work has commenced, full refunds may not always be applicable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Digital Nature -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Digital Nature of Services</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP provides customized digital services (such as resume writing and profile optimization). As such, once a project begins, intellectual work and time are invested immediately, making complete refunds impractical unless due to non-performance or system errors.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Process -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Refund Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-500/40">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-300 mb-4">Step-by-Step Refund Procedure</h3>
              <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4">
                <li><strong>Submit Request:</strong> Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-teal-300 hover:underline">info@optyp.com</a>.</li>
                <li><strong>Provide Details:</strong> Include order ID, package name, and reason for refund.</li>
                <li><strong>Review:</strong> Our support team reviews your request within 5 business days.</li>
                <li><strong>Resolution:</strong> Refunds are processed within 7–10 business days after approval.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-yellow-500/40">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">Information Required for Refund Requests</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Full name and registered email</li>
                <li>Transaction/Order ID</li>
                <li>Service package name</li>
                <li>Reason for refund and supporting documents (if applicable)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Partial Refund -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Partial Refunds</h2>
          <p>Partial refunds may be approved under the following scenarios:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Project partially completed before cancellation.</li>
            <li>Scope change initiated mid-project.</li>
            <li>Specific deliverables not meeting defined quality benchmarks.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
            All partial refund amounts are evaluated case-by-case and communicated transparently.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Refund Methods & Timeline -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Refund Methods & Timeline</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/10 text-teal-300">
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Payment Method</th>
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Refund Timeline</th>
                  <th class="py-2 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Processing Fee</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Credit Card</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">5–10 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Debit Card</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">3–7 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Digital Wallets</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">1–3 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">No fee</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Bank Transfer</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">3–5 business days</td>
                  <td class="py-2 px-4">Subject to banking fees</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Additional Legal Clauses -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Additional Legal Clauses</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>No Chargeback Policy:</strong> Clients agree not to file chargebacks or payment disputes before contacting OPTYP for resolution.</li>
            <li><strong>Force Majeure:</strong> Refunds are not applicable in events beyond our control (natural disasters, cyber incidents, etc.).</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> This policy aligns with India’s Consumer Protection Act and applicable global e-commerce laws.</li>
            <li><strong>Currency:</strong> All refunds are processed in the original payment currency.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Amendments & Jurisdiction -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Policy Amendments & Jurisdiction</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP reserves the right to update or modify this Refund Policy at any time without prior notice. Updated policies will be reflected on this page with an updated date.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            This policy shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <strong>India</strong>. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in <strong>Hyderabad, Telangana</strong>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-green-500 text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need Assistance with a Refund?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Our dedicated support team is here to help resolve your concerns swiftly and fairly.</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Contact Page:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">Visit Our Contact Page</a></p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-200 text-sm">Typical response time: within 24 hours (Mon–Fri).</p>
        </section>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Structured Data for SEO -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "RefundPolicy",
    "name": "OPTYP Refund Policy",
    "url": "https://optyp.github.io/refund/",
    "description": "Detailed refund terms and conditions for OPTYP's professional services, outlining eligibility, process, and refund timelines.",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "OPTYP",
      "url": "https://optyp.github.io",
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "email": "info@optyp.com",
        "contactType": "Customer Support",
        "availableLanguage": ["English"]
      },
      "sameAs": [
        "https://linkedin.com/company/optyp",
        "https://instagram.com/optyp",
        "https://facebook.com/optyp"
      ]
    },
    "applicableCountry": "IN"
  }
  </script>

  <style>
    .glass-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    article a {
      color: #5eead4;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    article a:hover {
      color: #86efac;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * {
        animation-duration: 0ms !important;
        transition-duration: 0ms !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
